Templates.name: sap.fe.test.BaseArrangements
Templates.helpDescription: All common arrangements (Given) for all Opa tests are defined here.

Templates.name: sap.fe.test.JourneyRunner
Templates.helpDescription: A JourneyRunner for executing integration tests with given settings.

Templates.name: sap.fe.test.JourneyRunner.run
Templates.helpDescription:
Executes the journeys in the given order.

The settings provided as first parameter are merged into the base settings of the JourneyRunner instance.

Templates.name: sap.fe.test.ListReport
Templates.helpDescription:
Provides a test page definition for a list report page with the corresponding parameters. Sample usage: 
var oListReportDefinition = new ListReport({ appId: "MyApp", componentId: "MyListReportId", entitySet: "MyEntitySet" });

Templates.name: sap.fe.test.ObjectPage
Templates.helpDescription:
Provides a test page definition for an object page with the corresponding parameters. Sample usage: 
var oObjectPageDefinition = new ObjectPage({ appId: "MyApp", componentId: "MyObjectPageId", entitySet: "MyEntitySet" });
